                        <interp inst="t18380917-name-592" type="given" value="JAMES"></interp>JAMES FARRER</persName>
                  </hi>. I am an apprentice at this house. I missed this pin a fortnight before Whitsuntide, out of my box.</p>
               <p>(The prisoner received a good character.)</p>
